    "igdbPublisher": "Atari, Inc.",
    "igdbSummary": "The Matrix: Path of Neo will follow the story of the blockbuster motion picture trilogy The Matrix, The Matrix Reloaded and The Matrix Revolutions and for the first time allow gamers to play as \"Neo\" and become \"The One.\"\nGamers will play as \"Neo,\" but from the moment the game begins, how the situations play out, how they handle them, how they deal with the events, where they go, how people react to them - it's all up to the gamer. They may win where \"Neo\" failed or find another way to solve the problem - the path is now theirs to follow.",
    "igdbFranchise": "The Matrix"
